{"tid":2038653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】邱騰華：美國撤香港特殊待遇　無損港國際金融中心地位","createTime":"2020-05-27T16:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T17:25:11.000Z","uid":13663,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e7af2816ecbb1785ea931bd7c963dbe9089e0764","tid":2038653,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"經濟脈搏 23:30 2020/05/26 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華接受《日經亞洲評論》訪問時表示，美國沒有單方面給予香港優惠待遇。香港是一個自由港，通過敞開大門來贏得地位。這不是任何人的禮物，這是公平的交易。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華強調，可以向國際社會保證，香港將維護法治，自由，保持競爭力和最自由的市場的位置；他並指，如果剝奪香港的地位，美國也會遭受痛苦，因為由此產生的貿易壁壘將影響兩地的貿易平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Knc5oJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnc5oJ2.png&h=78fe7df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d6e13edb922b1286a8120171857d2a866f71f6","tid":2038653,"uid":37528,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"如果剝奪香港的地位，美國也會遭受痛苦<br />\n<br />\n唔爭氣笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403f9912954826eb87cab473e9237379b0eecc88","tid":2038653,"uid":57309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c7d6e13edb922b1286a8120171857d2a866f71f6","tid":2038653,"uid":37528,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"如果剝奪香港的地位，美國也會遭受痛苦<br />\n<br />\n唔爭氣笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"打我一巴, 你隻手會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b726ddb8